title: Moab 2016 Comanche Jeep
description:
If this pickup concept doesn’t make you feel anything, check your pulse. This is the Jeep Comanche. It is a modified Renegade sitting on 32"s.

Revealed at the 2016 Easter Jeep Safari in Moab, Utah.
